<br>
Got my butt to Neriak Third Gate, logged by the zone.<br>
Got on my lvl 5 DE Necro, made a pet, made a /pet attack hotkey.  Ran out of the building, hit the pet attack hotkey (while within range), pet attacked and got ripped apart and Tani, and he came running for me.  I got to the zone and waited.  It takes him a minute to find his way to the zone (thx crappy pathing).  My necro stood there and got smeared by Tani (doubles for 150, duel wields swords so dont worry bout getting backstabbed).  Logged my Rogue on and started picking.<br>
