I didnt get the note the first spawn so I had to get my necro and do it again.  So if you do this be sure to get your necros pet spell and give him a few bonechips.  Aggro'd him once, but the zone was 2 feet away so didnt hurt too much.<br>
<br>
I did /petition a GM before I did this and it was A-ok with him so you wont get in any trouble like you would if you did the roof sploit. <br>
<br>
Viladar<br>
